snippet.title: Gravulse - Second Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Gravulse, an innovative space curvature laboratory that is trying to turn the laws of physics around, literally.
Plunge into the atmosphere of passing tests, with a new physics puzzle, where everything is based on gravity and magnetic properties.
Rather add to your wishlist if you liked the game!

Gravulse in Steam  - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1465210/Gravulse/
Gravulse in Twitter - https://twitter.com/gravulse

Gravulse в ВКонтакте - https://vk.com/gravulse
